      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5684292/" class="title-link">【读史记】淮阴侯韩信与韩王韩信</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5684292"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/66796306/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u66796306-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66796306/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">林九九</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-04"
