        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24367092/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24367092/" class="">【汉书】高后吕雉</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/66796306/" class=" " title="林九九">林九九</a>
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24367092">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24367092/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p24367092-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">通篇前三分之一讲自然灾害、诸侯王去世，后三分之二讲吕雉死后如何灭吕、立新帝。结尾却牛头不对马嘴地来了这么一段，据说还是照搬司马迁的......嘻，班固真TM是个人才。

</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-02-03 12:28</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                通篇前三分之一讲自然灾害、诸侯王去世，后三分之二讲吕雉死后如何灭吕、立新帝。结尾却牛头不对马嘴地来了这么一段，据说还是照搬司马迁的......嘻，班固真TM是个人才。
<div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p24367092-1.jpg" alt=""><br><span class="pic-title"></span></div>

